#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "What is a CMP?"
msgstr "Wat is een CMP?"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"A CMP manages cookie consent on your website. It shows the cookie banner, "
"stores visitor choices, and allows or blocks analytics scripts based on "
"consent."
msgstr ""
"Een CMP beheert cookietoestemming op uw website. Het toont de cookiebanner, "
"bewaart bezoekerskeuzes en staat analytics-scripts toe of blokkeert ze op "
"basis van toestemming."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Voorbeelden:"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"In your CMP, block the BimBeau Privacy Analytics advanced stats script until "
"the Statistics or Analytics purpose is accepted."
msgstr ""
"Blokkeer in uw CMP het BimBeau Privacy Analytics-script voor geavanceerde "
"statistieken totdat het doel Statistieken of Analytics is geaccepteerd."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Advanced stats are disabled. BimBeau Privacy Analytics will only use "
"essential stats."
msgstr ""
"Geavanceerde statistieken zijn uitgeschakeld. BimBeau Privacy Analytics "
"gebruikt alleen essentiële statistieken."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Respect DNT / GPC"
msgstr "DNT / GPC respecteren"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Stop measurement when the visitor’s browser sends a Do Not Track or Global "
"Privacy Control signal."
msgstr ""
"Stop met meten wanneer de browser van de bezoeker een Do Not Track- of "
"Global Privacy Control-signaal verzendt."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Visit measurement"
msgstr "Bezoekmeting"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Defines how long visitor activity can remain grouped under the same visitor "
"row before a new row is started after inactivity."
msgstr ""
"Bepaalt hoelang bezoekersactiviteit onder dezelfde bezoekersrij gegroepeerd "
"kan blijven voordat na inactiviteit een nieuwe rij wordt gestart."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Visitor activity window"
msgstr "Activiteitsvenster voor bezoekers"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Defines how long activity from the same visitor can remain grouped into one "
"visitor row. After this period of inactivity, BimBeau Privacy Analytics "
"starts a new visitor row. Range: 300 to 86400 seconds (5 minutes to 24 "
"hours)."
msgstr ""
"Bepaalt hoelang activiteit van dezelfde bezoeker in één bezoekersrij "
"gegroepeerd kan blijven. Na deze periode van inactiviteit start BimBeau "
"Privacy Analytics een nieuwe bezoekersrij. Bereik: 300 tot 86400 seconden (5 "
"minuten tot 24 uur)."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "URLs & campaigns"
msgstr "URL's en campagnes"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Control URL cleanup behavior and keep only campaign query parameters that "
"should remain available for attribution."
msgstr ""
"Beheer het gedrag voor URL-opschoning en bewaar alleen campagne-"
"queryparameters die beschikbaar moeten blijven voor attributie."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Clean URL query parameters"
msgstr "URL-queryparameters opschonen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Remove query parameters from tracked URLs."
msgstr "Verwijder queryparameters uit gevolgde URL's."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Allowed query parameters"
msgstr "Toegestane queryparameters"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Comma-separated list of allowed query keys (used for URL tracking and UTM "
"aggregation)."
msgstr ""
"Door komma's gescheiden lijst met toegestane querysleutels (gebruikt voor "
"URL-tracking en UTM-aggregatie)."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Data retention"
msgstr "Gegevensbewaring"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Choose how long to keep temporary detailed events, report details, and long-"
"term totals, then how often cleanup runs."
msgstr ""
"Choose how long to keep temporary detailed events, report details, and long-"
"term totals, then how often cleanup runs."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Temporary detailed events retention (days)"
msgstr "Bewaartermijn tijdelijke gedetailleerde gebeurtenissen (dagen)"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Used mainly for real-time and diagnostics. Not related to Debug mode."
msgstr "Used mainly for real-time and diagnostics. Not related to Debug mode."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Report details retention"
msgstr "Bewaartermijn rapportdetails"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Keeps detailed report dimensions such as pages, referrers, countries, "
"devices, and visitor details."
msgstr ""
"Keeps detailed report dimensions such as pages, referrers, countries, "
"devices, and visitor details."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Long-term totals retention"
msgstr "Bewaartermijn langetermijntotalen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Keeps anonymous daily totals for dashboard KPIs and the page views/visitors "
"chart after report details expire."
msgstr ""
"Keeps anonymous daily totals for dashboard KPIs and the page views/visitors "
"chart after report details expire."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Cleanup permanently removes expired details, while long-term totals remain "
"available until their own retention window ends."
msgstr ""
"Cleanup permanently removes expired details, while long-term totals remain "
"available until their own retention window ends."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Automatic cleanup frequency"
msgstr "Automatische opschoonfrequentie"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Defines how often WordPress checks for expired analytics data."
msgstr "Defines how often WordPress checks for expired analytics data."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Exclusions"
msgstr "Uitsluitingen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Select roles to exclude from tracking. Select all roles to ignore all logged-"
"in users."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer rollen om uit te sluiten van tracking. Selecteer alle rollen om "
"alle ingelogde gebruikers te negeren."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "No roles available."
msgstr "Geen rollen beschikbaar."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Debug"
msgstr "Debug"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Enable diagnostic output for troubleshooting tracking events, realtime "
"visitor detection, and REST payloads in the browser console and wp-content/"
"debug.log."
msgstr ""
"Schakel diagnostische uitvoer in voor het oplossen van problemen met "
"trackinggebeurtenissen, realtime bezoekersdetectie en REST-payloads in de "
"browserconsole en wp-content/debug.log."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Debug mode"
msgstr "Debugmodus"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Writes detailed diagnostic logs to the console and to wp-content/debug.log "
"when WordPress debug logging is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Schrijft gedetailleerde diagnostische logs naar de console en naar wp-"
"content/debug.log wanneer WordPress debug-logging is ingeschakeld."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Cleanup actions"
msgstr "Opschoningsacties"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Run retention cleanup immediately to remove only data older than the "
"configured retention window."
msgstr ""
"Voer bewaartermijnopschoning direct uit om alleen gegevens te verwijderen "
"die ouder zijn dan het geconfigureerde bewaartermijnvenster."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Run cleanup now"
msgstr "Opschoning nu uitvoeren"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Delete plugin tables on uninstall"
msgstr "Plugintabellen verwijderen bij de-installatie"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"When enabled, uninstalling BimBeau Privacy Analytics drops all plugin "
"analytics tables from the WordPress database."
msgstr ""
"Indien ingeschakeld verwijdert het de-installeren van BimBeau Privacy "
"Analytics alle analytics-tabellen van de plugin uit de WordPress-database."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Sensitive actions"
msgstr "Gevoelige acties"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Remove all aggregate KPI analytics, visitor-detail analytics, and raw log "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Verwijder alle geaggregeerde KPI-analytics, bezoekersdetail-analytics en "
"ruwe logregels."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Delete all analytics data"
msgstr "Alle analyticsgegevens verwijderen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Events configuration"
msgstr "Gebeurtenisconfiguratie"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "Instellingen opslaan"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Opslaan"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Confirm data purge"
msgstr "Wissen van gegevens bevestigen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"This action permanently removes all stored analytics and raw logs. Settings "
"remain unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Deze actie verwijdert permanent alle opgeslagen analytics en ruwe logs. "
"Instellingen blijven ongewijzigd."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "I confirm that I want to permanently purge all analytics data."
msgstr "Ik bevestig dat ik alle analyticsgegevens permanent wil wissen."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Purge now"
msgstr "Nu wissen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Confirm aggregated data purge"
msgstr "Wissen van geaggregeerde gegevens bevestigen"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"This action runs retention cleanup immediately and removes only rows older "
"than the configured window."
msgstr ""
"Deze actie voert bewaartermijnopschoning direct uit en verwijdert alleen "
"rijen die ouder zijn dan het geconfigureerde venster."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"I confirm that I want to purge only data older than the configured retention "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Ik bevestig dat ik alleen gegevens wil wissen die ouder zijn dan het "
"geconfigureerde bewaartermijnvenster."

